features: 3 YUMMY FACE MASKS TO EXFOLIATE & PAMPER - No need to wait for your birthday, treat your skin to a guilt-free sweet-scented peel off mask, mixed with plant-based sprinkles that gently exfoliate your skin
PACKED WITH NATURAL INGREDIENTS - 7th Heaven's Birthday Cake moisturising face masks are made with vanilla which helps to moisturise your face and leave it feeling completely refreshed

SUITABLE FOR ALL SKIN TYPES - This face mask set is suitable for all skin types, ensuring brighter skin for everyone. What's more, these soothing face peel masks are vegan and cruelty-free, so you can feel good about pampering yourself
CONVENIENT & MESS-FREE – Simply apply a facial mask to dry, cleansed skin. Relax and leave it to dry for 15-20 minutes as it works its magic, then gently peel off to reveal a glow worth celebrating

GENUINE 7TH HEAVEN SKINCARE – For over 30 years, 7th Heaven has made the world a happier place for both humans & animals. Their cruelty-free beauty products are inspired by nature’s treasures, with no hidden nasties, just pure goodness
